                                "start": 0,
                                "stop": 15.606,
                                "byte_start": 28672,
                                "byte_stop": 91157,
                                "text": "The judgment and opinion of the Court in the Regional Rail Reorganization Act Cases, 74-165 and the related cases, will be announced by Mr. Justice Brennan."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 15.606,
                        "stop": 102.837,
                        "byte_start": 91157,
                        "byte_stop": 440048,
                        "speaker": {
                            "ID": 15140,
                            "name": "William J. Brennan, Jr.",
                            "href": "https:\/\/api.oyez.org\/people\/william_j_brennan_jr",
                            "last_name": "Brennan",
                            "roles": [
                                {
                                    "id": 2786,
                                    "type": "scotus_justice",
                                    "date_start": -416862000,
                                    "date_end": 648450000,
                                    "appointing_president": "Dwight D. Eisenhower",
                                    "role_title": "Associate Justice of the Supreme Court of the United States",
                                    "institution_name": "Supreme Court of the United States",
                                    "href": "https:\/\/api.oyez.org\/preson_role\/scotus_justice\/2786"
                                }
                            ],
                            "thumbnail": {
                                "id": 32778,
                                "mime": "image\/png",
                                "size": 56873,
                                "href": "https:\/\/api.oyez.org\/sites\/default\/files\/william_j_brennan.png"
                            },
                            "length_of_service": 12330,
                            "identifier": "william_j_brennan_jr"
                        },
                        "text_blocks": [
                            {
                                "start": 15.606,
                                "stop": 36.039,
                                "byte_start": 91157,
                                "byte_stop": 172868,
                                "text": "These are three appeals and a cross-appeal from a judgment of a three-judge District Court for the Eastern District of Pennsylvania that declared unconstitutional the Regional Rail Reorganization Act of 1973 and enjoined its enforcement."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 36.039,
                                "stop": 70.897,
                                "byte_start": 172868,
                                "byte_stop": 312362,
                                "text": "The ground of the decision was that the Rail Act would affect a taking for public use without just compensation of the rail properties of the bankrupt Penn-Central Railroad because the Rail Act precluded a suit against the United States in the Court of Claims under the Tucker Act for a cash award in the amount of any shortfall from the constitutional minimum in the securities provided by the Rail Act to be paid for the rail properties."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 70.897,
                                "stop": 72.658,
                                "byte_start": 312362,
                                "byte_stop": 319363,
                                "text": "We reverse."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 72.658,
                                "stop": 80.206,
                                "byte_start": 319363,
                                "byte_stop": 349560,
                                "text": "We hold that the Rail Act does not preclude a Tucker Act remedy for any shortfall that may occur."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 80.206,
                                "stop": 90.789,
                                "byte_start": 349560,
                                "byte_stop": 391879,
                                "text": "Mr. Justice Douglas dissents and has filed a dissenting opinion on three ground one of which is that the Tucker Act remedy is not available."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 90.789,
                                "stop": 102.837,
                                "byte_start": 391879,
                                "byte_stop": 440048,
                                "text": "Mr. Justice Stewart also dissents and has filed a statement agreeing substantially with Justice Douglas\u0027 reasons why the Tucker Act remedy is not available."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
